General.Name: East Star Resources PLC
General.Description: East Star Resources Plc focuses on the discovery and development of gold, copper, and rare earth metals in Kazakhstan. It undertakes an exploration program, including nine licenses covering 1,321.5 square kilometer in three mineral districts. The company was formerly known as East Star Resources Limited and changed its name to East Star Resources Plc in March 2021. East Star Resources Plc was incorporated in 2020 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
